name: Testgeobuiz
body: Geospatial Media's offerings stand true for its mission statement through multiple media channels - print, online, video and social media. Our flagship products are under the brand names - Geospatial World (print magazine and web portal), GeoInt (print magazine and web portal) and GeoBuiz (live & on-demand video portal).
